lead_paragraph: Michael Phelps won the 200-meter butterfly at the Arena Pro Swim meet Friday night, where wind gusts up to 30 mph whipped up the water and created challenging conditions.

headline.main: Blowin' in the Wind: Phelps Wins 200 Fly at Arizona Meet
